    <time class="comment-date" datetime="2019-06-17 15:50:35">June 17, 2019 at 3:50 pm </time>
    
    &nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="#" class="toggle-replies-btn" data-toggle="hide">Hide Replies</a>
    <span class="comment-number"><a class="permalink" href="#blog-comment-159951487" title="Permalink to this comment" rel="nofollow">4</a></span>
  </div><!-- /.byline -->

  <div class="comment-content">
    <p>The right of the people to be secure in their persons, houses, papers, and effects, against unreasonable searche[s and s]eizures, shall not be violated, and no Warrants shall issue, but upon probable cause, supported by Oath or affirmation, and particularly describing the place to be searched, and the persons or things to be seized.</p>

  </div><!-- /.comment-content -->

  
