    <span class="comment-number"><a class="permalink" href="#blog-comment-159951549" title="Permalink to this comment" rel="nofollow">33</a></span>
  </div><!-- /.byline -->

  <div class="comment-content">
    <p>At least he wrote our dotard a very nice letter.</p>

  </div><!-- /.comment-content -->

  
